      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor, faint scratches and a few tiny stone chips on the hood that are typical for a car of this age. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffing on the door sills, but all electronics and features are fully functional. It drives smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
