      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that honors its engineering heritage. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects meticulous stewardship. Mechanically uncompromising and aesthetically superior, this represents an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
